    "description": "<p>LS 2 Services started with the goal of building Long-term and Sustainable relationships with our partners- the Community, Customers, Suppliers and Employees.</p>\n<p>From the firm's establishment, having the foresight to see the importance of building and maintaining stable liaison with partners in the cleaning eco-system is paramount to our business success.</p>\n<p>In the continual process of improvement,&nbsp;LS 2 Services' growth and transformation as a locally recognized cleaning company over the years has seen us adapting to a more technology-driven industry.</p>\n<p>The firm's administrative history builds our foundation and serves as a guide in our growth process. The meaning of&nbsp;LS 2 Services is embedded in our culture and will accompany us as we evolve.</p>",
